      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "bg_title",
          "left": 60,
          "top": 30,
          "width": 880,
          "height": 60,
          "rotate": 0,
          "content": "<p style=\"font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #333333;\">研究背景</p>",
          "defaultFontName": "",
          "defaultColor": "#333333",
          "textType": "title",
          "lineHeight": 1.2,
          "paragraphSpace": 5
        },
        {
          "type": "shape",
          "id": "bg_line",
          "left": 60,
          "top": 95,
          "width": 120,
          "height": 4,
          "viewBox": [200, 200],
          "path": "M 0 0 L 200 0",
          "fill": "#5b9bd5",
          "fixedRatio": false,
          "rotate": 0
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "bg_text1",
          "left": 60,
          "top": 130,
          "width": 880,
          "height": 100,
          "rotate": 0,
          "content": "<p style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.8;\">• 传统序列到序列模型（Seq2Seq）依赖 RNN/LSTM，存在长距离依赖问题</p><p style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.8;\">• 注意力机制（Attention）缓解了部分问题，但无法并行化训练</p><p style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.8;\">• Transformer 提出纯注意力架构，彻底摆脱循环结构，实现并行计算</p>",
          "defaultFontName": "",
          "defaultColor": "#333333",
          "textType": "content",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "paragraphSpace": 5
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "bg_text2",
          "left": 60,
          "top": 300,
          "width": 880,
          "height": 200,
          "rotate": 0,
          "content": "<p style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; color: #5b9bd5;\">现有方法的不足</p><p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 10px;\">1. RNN 序列计算导致训练速度慢，难以利用大规模数据</p><p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.8;\">2. 长距离信息衰减严重，翻译质量随句子长度下降</p><p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.8;\">3. 模型容量受限，无法充分利用 GPU 并行计算能力</p>",
          "defaultFontName": "",
          "defaultColor": "#333333",
          "textType": "content",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "paragraphSpace": 8
        }
      ],
      "background": { "type": "solid", "color": "#ffffff" }
    },
    {
      "id": "slide_method",
      "type": "content",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "method_title",
          "left": 60,
          "top": 30,
          "width": 880,
          "height": 60,
          "rotate": 0,
          "content": "<p style=\"font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #333333;\">方法概述：Self-Attention 机制</p>",
          "defaultFontName": "",
          "defaultColor": "#333333",
          "textType": "title",
          "lineHeight": 1.2,
          "paragraphSpace": 5
        },
        {
          "type": "shape",
          "id": "method_line",
          "left": 60,
          "top": 95,
          "width": 200,
          "height": 4,
          "viewBox": [200, 200],
          "path": "M 0 0 L 200 0",
          "fill": "#5b9bd5",
          "fixedRatio": false,
          "rotate": 0
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "method_desc",
          "left": 60,
          "top": 130,
          "width": 880,
          "height": 120,
          "rotate": 0,
          "content": "<p style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.8;\">Transformer 的核心是自注意力机制（Self-Attention），通过 Q、K、V 三个矩阵计算词与词之间的关联权重，使模型能够捕捉长距离依赖关系。</p>",
          "defaultFontName": "",
          "defaultColor": "#333333",
          "textType": "content",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "paragraphSpace": 5
        },
        {
          "type": "shape",
          "id": "method_box",
          "left": 60,
          "top": 280,
          "width": 880,
          "height": 250,
          "viewBox": [200, 200],
          "path": "M 0 0 L 200 0 L 200 200 L 0 200 Z",
          "fill": "#f0f7ff",
          "fixedRatio": false,
          "rotate": 0,
          "outline": { "style": "solid", "width": 2, "color": "#5b9bd5" }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "method_steps",
          "left": 100,
          "top": 300,
          "width": 800,
          "height": 210,
          "rotate": 0,
          "content": "<p style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #5b9bd5;\">Self-Attention 计算步骤</p><p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #444444; line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 10px;\">1. 输入序列 X 分别通过三个线性变换得到 Q（Query）、K（Key）、V（Value）</p><p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #444444; line-height: 1.8;\">2. 计算 Q 与 K 的点积，除以 √d_k，进行缩放防止梯度消失</p><p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #444444; line-height: 1.8;\">3. 经过 Softmax 归一化得到注意力权重矩阵</p><p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #444444; line-height: 1.8;\">4. 权重与 V 相乘，得到加权求和的输出表示</p>",
          "defaultFontName": "",
          "defaultColor": "#333333",
          "textType": "content",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "paragraphSpace": 5
        }
      ],
      "background": { "type": "solid", "color": "#ffffff" }
    },
    {
      "id": "slide_formula",
      "type": "content",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "formula_title",
          "left": 60,
          "top": 30,
          "width": 880,
          "height": 60,
          "rotate": 0,
          "content": "<p style=\"font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #333333;\">核心公式</p>",
          "defaultFontName": "",
          "defaultColor": "#333333",
          "textType": "title",
          "lineHeight": 1.2,
          "paragraphSpace": 5
        },
        {
          "type": "shape",
          "id": "formula_line",
          "left": 60,
          "top": 95,
          "width": 120,
          "height": 4,
          "viewBox": [200, 200],
          "path": "M 0 0 L 200 0",
          "fill": "#5b9bd5",
          "fixedRatio": false,
          "rotate": 0
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "formula_desc",
          "left": 60,
          "top": 130,
          "width": 880,
          "height": 60,
          "rotate": 0,
          "content": "<p style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #333333;\">Scaled Dot-Product Attention 公式：</p>",
          "defaultFontName": "",
          "defaultColor": "#333333",
          "textType": "content",
          "lineHeight": 1.5,
          "paragraphSpace": 5
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "formula_main",
          "left": 150,
          "top": 200,
          "width": 700,
          "height": 120,
          "rotate": 0,
          "content": "<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 36px; color: #333333;\">Attention(Q, K, V) = softmax(QK<sup>T</sup> / √d<sub>k</sub>)V</p>",
          "defaultFontName": "",
          "defaultColor": "#333333",
          "textType": "content",
          "lineHeight": 1.2,
          "paragraphSpace": 5
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "formula_explain",
          "left": 60,
          "top": 340,
          "width": 880,
          "height": 180,
          "rotate": 0,
          "content": "<p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.8;\">• <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Q（Query）</span>：查询向量，表示当前词对其他词的关注需求</p><p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.8;\">• <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">K（Key）</span>：键向量，表示被查询词的索引信息</p><p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.8;\">• <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">V（Value）</span>：值向量，包含被查询词的实际内容信息</p><p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.8;\">• <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">√d<sub>k</sub></span>：缩放因子，防止点积过大导致 Softmax 梯度消失</p>",
          "defaultFontName": "",
          "defaultColor": "#333333",
          "textType": "content",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "paragraphSpace": 5
        }
      ],
      "background": { "type": "solid", "color": "#ffffff" }
    },
